2026-05-11T03:57:43.4766324Z 26            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-11T03:57:43.4766585Z 27          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-11T03:57:43.4766933Z 28            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-11T03:57:43.4767288Z 29        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-11T03:57:43.4767639Z 30        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-11T03:57:43.4767947Z 31        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-11T03:57:43.4768118Z 32    -->
